headline: Assessing Baxter International (BAX) Valuation After Recent Share Price Momentum And Margin Concerns
summary: Baxter International (BAX) has drawn fresh investor attention after recent trading, with the share price at $19.50 and mixed returns over the month and past 3 months prompting closer scrutiny of its fundamentals. See our latest analysis for Baxter International. The recent 1 day share price return of 2.04% and 1 month share price return of 5.18% sit against a 1 year total shareholder return decline of 33.07%.
